      <title>第六街财团将收购瑞银抵押贷款部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/sixth-street-consortium-said-to-be-buyer-of-ubs-mortgage-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由 Sixth Street Partners 牵头的一组投资者已同意从瑞银集团手中收购瑞士信贷的美国抵押贷款服务业务。]]></description>
