      <title>亚洲信贷交易蓬勃发展，千禧年银行开设新加坡办事处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/millennium-opens-singapore-office-as-asia-credit-trading-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[千禧顾问公司 (Millennium Advisors) 已将其交易和销售业务扩展到亚洲，以利用该地区对电子交易和美元债券日益增长的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/millennium-opens-singapore-office-as-asia-credit-trading-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
