      <title>索罗斯和德鲁肯米勒在股市崩盘前减持大型股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/soros-druckenmiller-pared-megacap-holdings-ahead-of-summer-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在今年科技股的火爆上涨行情转而于 7 月中旬遭遇大幅下滑之前，乔治·索罗斯 (George Soros) 和斯坦利·德鲁肯米勒 (Stanley Druckenmiller) 的投资公司削减了对“七侠荡寇志”股票的持股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/soros-druckenmiller-pared-megacap-holdings-ahead-of-summer-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 13:34:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员们放弃押注美联储大幅降息，因美国经济韧性十足</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/treasury-yields-rise-sharply-as-data-rules-out-big-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国经济强劲反弹促使交易员降低对美联储今年大幅降息的预期，随后美国国债收益率飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/treasury-yields-rise-sharply-as-data-rules-out-big-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 12:51:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国零售销售数据好于预期，新兴市场货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/emerging-market-currencies-hover-around-2-year-high-stocks-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在数据显示美国经济具有韧性之后，发展中国家货币走弱，令对美联储下个月将异常大幅降息的押注降温。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/emerging-market-currencies-hover-around-2-year-high-stocks-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 10:27:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗紧张局势和美国零售销售强劲推动油价止跌两日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对伊朗可能袭击以色列的担忧和强劲的美国经济数据掩盖了持续的需求担忧，油价在连续两天下跌后走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 23:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>零售销售缓解“增长恐慌” 股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asian-stocks-to-open-weaker-cpi-calms-wall-street-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[零售销售数据凸显了全球最大经济体的实力，导致股市上涨、债市下跌，缓解了人们对美联储高利率可能导致经济明显放缓的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-14/asian-stocks-to-open-weaker-cpi-calms-wall-street-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 22:36:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
